    firefox

ctrl + alt + x
    keepassxc

ctrl + alt + a
    xst aerc

ctrl + alt + s
    signal-desktop

ctrl + alt + t
    telegram-desktop

ctrl + alt + o
    libreoffice

ctrl + alt + k
    kitty

ctrl + alt + m
    xst musikcube

ctrl + alt + d
    discord

ctrl + alt + e
    element

ctrl + alt + c
    codium

